    <div class="story-text">
      <span class="meta-tag">Our Story</span>
      <h2>Rooted in Brandon. Engineered for Florida.</h2>
      <p>Originally established in Brandon, Florida, <strong>Building Home</strong> operates under the direct
        professional management of Florida Certified Licensed General Contractor Gisselle Amparo. The firm was forged to
        bridge the gap between progressive architectural blueprints and the strict, unyielding engineering requirements
        necessary for High-Velocity Hurricane Zones (HVHZ) and coastal preservation.</p>
      <p>We do not take on minor cosmetic updates or light retail remodeling. Our field teams operate strictly within an
        engineered ground-up grid layout framework—maximizing structural energy efficiency, deploying high-impact
        hurricane glass barriers, and pouring monolithic structural concrete foundations designed to last centuries.</p>
      <p>Whether pouring foundations in Wesley Chapel, running massive commercial framing lines in Clearwater, or
        executing high-scale footprint expansions in Tampa, our construction management metrics enforce total compliance
        with strict Florida building standards.</p>
